    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Cut your<strong> lemon[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (don't like raw garlic? Go easy!), <strong>chopped parsley</strong>, <strong>clotted cream</strong> and a squeeze of <strong>lemon </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) in a small bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>garlic butter</strong></p>",
