    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim your <strong>green beans</strong></p><p>Once the potatoes are almost fork-tender, add your<strong> green beans</strong> to the pot and cook for a further 3-4 min or until tender with a bite</p><p>Once done, drain and return them to the pot with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, a squeeze of <strong>lemon </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>",
