      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>crispy chicken escalopes</strong> with the <strong>garlic butter</strong> – these are your<strong> garlicky chicken kiev</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>garlicky chicken kiev</strong> with the <strong>tender green beans </strong>and <strong>potatoes </strong>to the side, and garnish with a<strong> lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
